summary: This appears to be a forwarding email from the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS) containing a daily transcript dated June 18, 2019, related to the Jeffrey Epstein case. The email includes an attachment of the transcript file.

events.title: Daily Transcript Production
events.description: A daily transcript related to the Jeffrey Epstein case was produced, likely from court proceedings or a deposition.

keyFacts: The document is an email forwarding a daily transcript related to the Jeffrey Epstein case.
The transcript is dated June 18, 2019, and was forwarded on June 19, 2019.
The email originates from and is sent to the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
The attached transcript file is named 'SNY.NY.0618.19.AY.pdf'.
The document identifier is EFTA00096209, which is part of Data Set 9 of released documents.
